text: Manuel González Millán (born 9 September 1982) is a Spanish football manager and former player who is the manager of Gimnástica Segoviana CF. ==Club career== Manu started his profession football career through Rayo Majadahonda in 2003 and after one season he joined S.S. Reyes in 2005 and stayed for two seasons and left the club in 2007. ==Managerial career== In 2018 Manu appointed as the head coach of the Spanish club Segoviana. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Madrilenian footballers Category:Segunda División B players Category:Spanish football managers Category:CF Rayo Majadahonda players Category:UD San Sebastián de los Reyes players
